items.title: HAL upgraded to ŌĆśMaharatnaŌĆÖ status, becomes 14th PSU to join elite group
items.description: India now has 14 "Maharatna" public sector undertakings (PSUs), including prominent names such as BHEL, BPCL, Coal India, GAIL, HPCL, Indian Oil, NTPC, ONGC, Power Grid, SAIL, Oil India, REC, PFC, and the recently upgraded Hindustan Aeronautics Limited (HAL).
